      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Political Science              : An examination of political institutions and processes in today's Europe, concentrating on the member-states of the European Union and on the Union itself. The course is organized thematically rather than on a country-by-country basis.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Winter 2015          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Filippo Sabetti (Winter)                  </p>

    
